// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1372 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 167af747-dc3e-518f-9365-bc57772514ee

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
